## Infrastructure Hardening

### Nginx Configuration

Updated `examples/nginx/nginx-aitbc.conf` to match production deployment:
- Added `default_server` directive
- Set real hostname: `aitbc3.aitbc.bubuit.net`
- Added `/peertube/` location
- Added rewrite rules for `/api/` and `/whisper/`
- Removed outdated `.example` template

### Database

- Consolidated DB initialization: `storage.db.init_db()` + `storage.db.init_async_db()`
- Created `packages/aitbc-shared/` for shared ORM models
- Resolved SQLAlchemy table conflicts (MarketplaceBid, JobPayment, PaymentEscrow)

### Caching

- Fixed timezone-aware datetime comparisons in `cache_entry.py`
- All 46 caching tests passing
- `_generate_cache_key` properly exported

