## Breaking Changes

### Authentication

API keys are deprecated. All clients must migrate to JWT:

```python
# Before (deprecated)
headers = {"X-Api-Key": "your-api-key"}

# After (required)
headers = {"Authorization": f"Bearer {token}"}
```

### Blockchain

Testnet configuration no longer supported. Must use real mainnet RPC.

### Environment Variables

| Removed | Replacement |
|---------|-------------|
| `APP_ENV=dev` auth bypass | `settings.environment` with proper validation |
| `TEST_MODE=true` | Proper test fixtures |

