## Deployment Checklist

- [ ] Set `BLOCKCHAIN_RPC_URL` to mainnet RPC
- [ ] Deploy smart contracts to mainnet
- [ ] Configure `JWT_SECRET` (32+ byte random)
- [ ] Set `server_name` in nginx config
- [ ] Enable HTTPS (uncomment SSL block)
- [ ] Run `nginx -t && systemctl reload nginx`
- [ ] Verify all systemd services running
- [ ] Monitor auth failure rates
- [ ] Check blockchain confirmation times

